    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a dual-VANOS system meticulously serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency across the entire powerband. Every suspension bushing and mechanical linkage retains factory-new tolerances, delivering the telepathic handling and balanced longitudinal dynamics these E46 platforms are renowned for. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
