    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional-grade ceramic coating applied just last season; there are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, featuring supple leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned, a smoke-free environment, and original factory floor mats. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the advanced climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented from day one. It has never seen snow or salt, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly preserved specimen. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 44900.0,
