      "description": "Hi there! I'm so excited to share my pride and joy with you. This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It's super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready for your next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
