      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This vehicle boasts impeccable mechanical provenance, including documented Vanos system overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M-differential lock. The factory-original paint remains flawless, reflecting the meticulous climate-controlled storage this unit has received. No pixel degradation in the dash, no bolster wear, and a chassis that remains as rigid as the day it left Regensburg. A pure, analog driving experience for the discerning petrolhead.",
